  "description": "<h1>Active: Suppress</h1> Dispels both the wearer and the target. Enemy targets are slowed for %enemy_effect_duration% seconds. Allied targets gain bonus movespeed and %slow_resist%%% slow resistance for %ally_effect_duration% seconds. Caster is always granted the ally benefit on cast.<br><br>Both movement speed reduction and increase start at %phase_movement_speed%%% and gradually decrease to 0% over the course of the buff duration.<br>Dispel Type: <span class=\"GameplayValues GameplayVariable\">Basic Dispel</span>\n\n<h1>Passive: Manabreak</h1>Each attack burns %feedback_mana_burn% mana from the target, and deals %damage_per_burn% physical damage per burned mana. <br><br>Illusions do not burn mana.",
